Add_Dynamic_Module Storage Appeal_SQLite_Storage
Storage Debug 1
Storage Set_Paths ./Resources
Storage Open Test
Storage Set Audio.Volume 75
Storage Get Audio.Volume
Storage Insert Songs FolkSong "Billy Snyder"
Storage Insert Songs TestTrack "Appeal Storage Test"
Storage Find Songs FolkSong
Storage List Songs
Storage Begin
Storage Update Songs FolkSong "Billy Snyder Updated"
Storage Commit
Storage Find Songs FolkSong
Storage Export ./Resources/Storage/Test_Storage_Export.txt
Storage Backup ./Resources/Storage/Test_Backup.appealdb
Storage Remove Songs TestTrack
Storage List Songs
Storage Restore ./Resources/Storage/Test_Backup.appealdb
Storage List Songs
Storage Close Test
Done
